The '''2021 [[ICF World Junior and U23 Canoe Slalom Championships]]''' will take place in [[Auckland]], [[New Zealand]] under the auspices of the [[International Canoe Federation]] (ICF).<ref>{{cite web|title=2021 ICF JUNIOR & U23 CANOE SLALOM WORLD CHAMPIONSHIPS|url=https://www.canoeicf.com/canoe-slalom-world-championships/auckland-2021|website=CanoeICF.com|accessdate=24 February 2018}}</ref> It will be the 23rd edition of the competition for Juniors (U18) and the 10th edition for the Under 23 category. It will be the first global canoe slalom championships in New Zealand.
