{{PBA Awards}} The '''[[Philippine Basketball Association]] (PBA) All-Rookie Team''' is an annual [[Philippine Basketball Association]] (PBA) honor given since the [[2004–05 PBA season]], to the top rookie(s) of the season in each of the five [[basketball]] positions: [[point guard]], [[shooting guard]] (off-guard or big guard), [[small forward]], [[Power forward (basketball)|power forward]] and [[center (basketball)|center]].<ref>[http://www.spin.ph/basketball/pba/news/stanley-pringle-leads-all-rookie-team-to-be-honored-in-pba-press-corps-awards-night Stanley Pringle leads All-Rookie team to be honored in PBA Press Corps Awards Night], spin.ph, September 10, 2015</ref>
Unlike the traditional player awards, which is given by the league, this citation is awarded by the PBA Press Corps.
